    "steps": [
        "Take the onion and tomato; chop them finely and keep aside.",
        "Place a pan on the gas stove and turn on the flame (high).",
        "Add oil to the pan and heat it for 2 min.",
        "Add chopped onion in the pan and stir till golden brown.",
        "Add ginger garlic paste in the pan and mix for 1 min.",
        "Add all the masalas (spices) in the pan and mix properly.",
        "Add the washed chicken to the mixture and cook for 5 min until excess water is soaked.",
        "Add 250ml water, cover the pan with lid, and turn the flame to medium.",
        "Cook the chicken for 15 min until cooked properly, stirring in between.",
